                  <p>Fig. 2 <a href="https://www.harvardartmuseums.org/tour/drawings-from-the-age-of-bruegel-rubens-and-rembrandt-the-complete-collection-online/slide/10047">Christian Benjamin Müller, after Peter Paul Rubens, <em>Saint Gregory of Nazianzus</em></a></p>
